    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "な…………なんだってーー！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wh…………Whatーー！？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "長瀬琴乃が、月のテンペストを再結成するだとーー！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono Nagase is going to reunite Moon Tempestーー！？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.2333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1366.6666666999995,
          "startTime": 5.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.0999090831
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "約束通り、解散しました\nでも、「再結成するな」とは言われていません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As promised‚ I disbanded the group.\nBut I was never told \"Don't reunite\".",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.8740589459
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Lemon",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02-lmn001.m4a",
      "text": "……あらあら、厚かましいわねぇ\nあなたって思っていた以上に、恥を知らないのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……My my‚ how shameless.\nYou really have no shame‚ do you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.8464178085
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02-lim001.m4a",
      "text": "……そんなわがまま、本気で通ると思ってんのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……Do you seriously think you can get away with that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.8464178085,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.7497738679
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "なんて言われようと構いません\n私は、本気です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't care what you say.\nI'm serious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.1854880493
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02-lim002.m4a",
      "text": "ハッ！ 馬鹿もここまで突き抜けると\nどうしようもねーな。……好きにしろ。興味が失せた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Stupid! That's it\nI can't help it. …… Do what you want. I've lost interest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.6894107342
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lim",
      "speakerName": "小南来夢",
      "speakerNameEn": "Laim",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lim.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02-lim003.m4a",
      "text": "だが、あたしらを踏み台にしたんだ\nその事実だけは忘れるんじゃねぇぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you used us as a stepping stone.\nDon't forget that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.1583905379
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Lemon",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02-lmn002.m4a",
      "text": "負け犬の世迷言を、世間はどう受け止めるのかしらぁ\n楽しみねぇ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How does the world accept the nonsense of a loser\nI'm looking forward to it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.1809984047
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_big4challengestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gpstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.3563138216
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "lmn",
      "speakerName": "大須賀れもん",
      "speakerNameEn": "Lemon",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-lmn.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02-lmn003.m4a",
      "text": "それはそうと、そろそろステージから降りてもらえる？\nここは、勝者が立つ場所だから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That aside‚ would you mind stepping off the stage?\nThis is the winner's spot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.3563138216,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
