      "text": "えっ……と……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um… well…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.2598597053,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "……黙っていても仕方ありませんね\n今後どうしていくか、みんなで話し合いましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……There's no point in staying silent.\nLet's all discuss what we're going to do from now on.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.6995959123,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "せっかく、{user}さんにも\n気を遣っていただきましたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since Manager-san\nwas kind enough to give us this opportunity…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.0127510303,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "ねぇ……その前に、琴乃ちゃんは\nどうして月ストに戻ろうって思ったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey… before that‚ Kotono…\n…why did you decide to return to Moon Tempest?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.2666707357,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうですわ！　私達もあの場でいきなり聞いて\nまだ気持ちの整理が出来ていませんのよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "T-that's right! We were all caught off guard hearing it there‚\nso we haven't had time to process it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.0681091786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "そう……だよね、ごめん。分かった、ちゃんと説明する\n私……みんなのステージを見て、気付いたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… you're right‚ I'm sorry. Okay‚ I'll explain properly.\nI… after seeing everyone's performance‚ I realized…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.9014425119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 175.0820942563
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "どりきゅんみたいに、心を鬼にして……\n相手を叩き潰すことが、私の求めていた強さじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…that crushing your opponents like DoriKyun…\n…isn't the kind of strength I was looking for.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.3681091786,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "みんなみたいに、諦めないで戦い続けて\n目をそらしていた私のことも……前を向かせてくれた",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You all kept fighting without giving up‚\nand even made me‚ who was looking away… face forward.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.2014425119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、これが本当の強さなんだって\nみんなが、教えてくれたの……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ this is true strength…\n…you all taught me that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 201.0347758453,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "そっか。私達のパフォーマンス……\nちゃんと、届いたんだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. Our performance…\n…it reached you.",
        "id": ""
