      "text": "琴乃ちゃんの気持ちは分かりました\nきちんと話してくれて、ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand how you feel‚ Kotono-chan.\nThank you for speaking to us honestly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 225.968147548,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02/sud_vo_adv_main_03_10_02-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "ですが……私はまだ、納得出来ていません\nそれは、みんなも同じはずです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… I'm still not convinced.\nI'm sure everyone else feels the same way.",
        "id": ""
